{"tid":344344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"游完水狂生暗瘡","createTime":"2017-08-02T08:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T08:30:23.000Z","uid":55438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc93eae8093da2cc91e39cf3905f1e821005150","tid":344344,"uid":55438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"本身諗住游水減肥<br />\n點知游完就瘋狂生暗瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265fd6113c8a5be479701cab5af989d8f53815e0","tid":344344,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"皮膚敏感"},{"pid":"b6389dbd463f5048dcd657aeec701a38981e7b61","tid":344344,"uid":62121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:30:23.000Z","msg":"1.泳池用氯消毒 氯會令你啲皮膚好乾無哂水份（皮膚太乾就會分泌油 令到你水油唔平衡 生暗瘡）<br />\n2.啲水始終都係污糟 雜質多 皮膚食哂<br />\n<br />\n建議你游完後 搵啲低敏既洗面奶/洗面啫喱（啫喱更溫和）洗乾淨塊面，同埋一定一定要即刻揸保濕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}